<html>
  <div
    style="display: table; background: #5e77da; color: #fff; text-align: center; align-items: center;
      border-radius: 0.5em; font-size: 1em; padding: 1em;
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', 'Noto Sans', 'Liberation Sans', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol', 'Noto Color Emoji';
      width: 95%; margin: 0 auto; align-items: center;"
  >
    <div>
      <%= email_image_tag("desktop-logo.png") %>
    </div>
    <p>Hey there, <strong><%= @user.username %></strong></p>

    <p>Can't remember your password for <strong><%= @user.email %></strong>? That's OK, it happens. Hit the link below to set a new one.</p>

    <p>
      <%= link_to "Reset my password", edit_identity_password_reset_url(sid: @signed_id),
      style:"background:#3454D1; border-color:#3454D1; color: white; border-radius: 0.375rem; padding: 6px 12px;
          text-decoration: none;" %>
    </p>
    <hr>
    <p>If you did not request a password reset you can safely ignore this email.</p>
  </div>
</html>